# E-Commerce Funnel Refactor: Product Recommendations System

## Overview
Transform the LOOKSMAXX advice system from diagnostic-only to an e-commerce funnel by implementing an "always-sell" product recommendation engine. Even users with perfect scores will receive product recommendations for maintenance.

## User Requirements
- âœ… Keep both products AND procedures
- âœ… Show products to EVERYONE (even ideal scores get maintenance products)
- âœ… Mixed affiliate approach (Amazon + direct brand links)
- âœ… Daily Stack as hero element (top of PlanTab)
- âœ… Use existing 6 categories from supplements.ts

---

## Architecture

### Current State
- **advice-engine.ts**: 10 procedural plans (surgical/minimally invasive/foundational)
- **supplements.ts**: 26 supplement products (DORMANT - not in UI)
- **Trigger logic**: Only fires for flaws (NOT ideal metrics)
- **UI**: PlanTab shows only procedures

### Target State
```
PlanTab.tsx
â”œâ”€ DailyStackCard (NEW - top hero element)
â”‚  â””â”€ 4-6 universal products for all users
â”œâ”€ PotentialScoreCard (existing)
â”œâ”€ Targeted Product Recommendations (NEW)
â”‚  â”œâ”€ State A: Corrective Products (flaw metrics)
â”‚  â””â”€ State B: Maintenance Products (ideal metrics)
â””â”€ Procedure Plans (existing - surgical/minimally invasive/foundational)
```

