## Notes

### Affiliate Link Format
**Amazon:**
```
https://amazon.com/dp/{ASIN}?tag=looksmaxx-20
```
Replace `looksmaxx-20` with actual Amazon Associates ID.

**Direct Brand (example):**
```
https://vitaminexpress.org/us/collagen-peptides?ref=looksmaxx
```

### FTC Disclosure
Add to every product card:
```
"We may earn a commission from purchases made through links on this page."
```

### Future Enhancements
- A/B test messaging (corrective vs preventative)
- Track which products convert best
- Add "Buy Complete Daily Stack" bundle link
- Email capture: "Send my Daily Stack to email"
- Personalized product bundles based on top 3 flaws
